description: Scale ca. 1:120,000. Title supplied. Oriented with north to the bottom. Relief shown pictorially. Pictorial map. Hummel purchase 1930, no. 34. Shows area along Qiantang River, especially the section of Hangzhou Bay in Zhejiang Province. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Previous call number: G7822.Q3A5 1820 .H3 Vault Shelf AACR2: 650/2; 700
